                :markdown

                    <br/>
                    #### Class Submodules
                    A class module can contain `<permission>` nodes and kits. Permission nodes give players with that class specific permissions. Players can be give any permission from any of the currently loaded plugins.

                        <class name="Leprachaun" description="Sticky XP Orbs with double jump!" longdescription="XP bar is a double-jump cooldown, use Bottle O' Enchanting to track enemies with XP orbs!" icon="exp bottle">
                            <!-- The classes permissions -->
                            <permission>gs.ability.agility</permission>
                            <!-- The classes kit -->
                            <kit parents="potions">
                                <item slot="0" amount="5" name="`a`lBottle o' Gold">exp bottle</item>
                                <item slot="2" amount="16">cooked beef</item>
                                <double-jump/>
                            </kit>
                        </class>

                    <br/>
